#*: {{...}} et vasa intulit in domum '''thesauri''' dei sui
#*:: "{{...}} and he brought the vessels into the '''treasure''' house of his god."
# a [[dear]] [[friend]], [[loved one]]
# a [[vault]] for treasure
# [[chest]], [[strongbox]]
# [[repository]], [[collection]]

