==Proto-Germanic==

===Etymology===
{{root|gem-pro|ine-pro|*preyH-}}
From {{inh|gem-pro|ine-pro|*priHós||beloved}}. The original meaning was probably something like “from one's own clan”, from which a meaning “being a free man, not a [[serf]]” developed.

